OL,5,G1100 Traffic Cops
OL,6,     FThe cops deal with a suicidal man
OL,7,     Fwith mental health problems, an
OL,8,     FEritrean woman dumped out of a
OL,9,     Florry by people traffickers, and a
OL,10,     Flass who's had a barney with her
OL,11,     Fboyfriend.
OL,12,G1200 Traffic Cops
OL,13,     FIn Leeds the cops are on the look
OL,14,     Fout for a stolen Ford Fiesta;
OL,15,     Ftheir hunt ending in a dramatic
OL,16,     Ffoot chase pursuing one of the
OL,17,     Fmouthiest criminals they've ever
OL,18,     Fseen.
