OL,5,G1300 Traffic Cops
OL,6,     FThe cops have their hands full
OL,7,     Fwith night time drink driving
OL,8,     Fincidents. Four police cars are
OL,9,     Fneeded to stop a car with a
OL,10,     Fmotorbike hanging out of the boot.
OL,11,G1400 Police Interceptors
OL,12,     FRunaway drivers are convinced to
OL,13,     Fstop by the threat of 50,000
OL,14,     Fvolts. A drink driver resists
OL,15,     Farrest, earning a face full of
OL,16,     Fincapacitating PAVA spray.
OL,17,G1500 Police Interceptors
OL,18,     FThe team chase a Golf GTI being
OL,19,     Fdriven at three times the legal
OL,20,     Flimit. Reports of gunshots at a
OL,21,     Fhouse party lead to a full-scale
OL,22,     Ffirearms operation.
